													<h6><a href="https://lithub.com/author/benjamincwaterhouse/">Benjamin C. Waterhouse</a></h6>
													Benjamin C. Waterhouse is the author of <em>Lobbying America: The Politics of Business from Nixon to NAFTA</em> and <em>The Land of Enterprise: A Business History of the United States</em>. He is a professor of history at the University of North Carolina at Chapel Hill.																									</div>
